com.bumptech.glide.annotation

Annotation Type GlideModule


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface GlideModule
    Identifies AppGlideModules and LibraryGlideModules for Glide's annotation processor to merge at compile time.

    Replaces tags in AndroidManifest.xml.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String glideName
      Returns the name of the class that will be used as a replacement for Glide in Applications that depend on Glide's generated code.

    • Element Detail

      • glideName

        public abstract String glideName
        Returns the name of the class that will be used as a replacement for Glide in Applications that depend on Glide's generated code.
        Default:
        "GlideApp"
